snippet.title: The Hunt: Championship Edition - Announce Trailer
snippet.description: The premier hunting game is arriving on Nintendo Switch on October 23rd!  Hunt like a Pro with immersive Nintendo Switch motion controls or use the authentic Bullseye Pro game rifle peripheral for a truly special shooting experience!
